The bazaar/nexus are spots for people to sit unharmed.  Its the place for gankers to go afk for a few hours and wait for manaburn to refresh so that they can port somewhere, burn, and instant nexus gate only to repeat the process.  Its the place where anyone is safe, and rallos stops becoming a PvP server.  It isn't a 95% pvp server, it should be all or nothing.  This is also the general consensus of at least the Rallos Zek community, pks and anti's alike.<br>
